扇门后面有汽车； 情况 2，主持人蒙提霍尔并不知道哪扇门后面有汽车，只不过碰巧打开了一扇没有汽车的门； 问，分别在这两种情况下，节目参与者是否应该更换自己的选择？ 本题已加入知乎「数学问答集市」>> 数学问答集市​www.zhihu.com/xen/market/ecom-page/1456341861586001920?theme=light 更多「数学」相关讨论欢迎关注。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-4f6d762fd391504c90098a167611c449_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "86 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/507955265"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4ItZTM4Ijp/vN7EAMaCDc1MTYwNTExIODtkI4GMAM4dUAZcgk1MDc5NTUyNjV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "26_1640963292.3278618", "card_id": "Q_449004406", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 99}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么千元机推荐都是小米？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-12c57ae70baa4b92b4093e887b2fb987_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "85 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/449004406"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8ItZTM4Ijp/vN7EAMaCDYyMDU3NjgwII/SrYIGMAY4pQFAGnIJNDQ5MDA0NDA2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "27_1640963292.3281672", "card_id": "Q_504370197", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 26}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "有好一点的过年文案吗?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "今年高三啦，马上过年了，想在高中最后一年给同学们买个横幅，激励祝福一下 (最好在 12 字以内，超过 12 字要补差价，哈哈哈哈嗝) 长一点也没关系哒，我应该有差价钱！哈哈哈哈嗝"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-f62cc1432df0ebd17cde176a9a5c079e_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "80 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/504370197"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4ItZTM4Ijp/vN7EAMaCDc0MzYzMjg5IKH1vI0GMAA4I0Abcgk1MDQzNzAxOTd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "28_